1400
01:29:45,630 --> 01:29:48,130
<i>Atenção, falha no regulador
de temperatura.</i>

1401
01:29:57,047 --> 01:29:58,088
<i>Sobrecarga.</i>

1402
01:29:58,172 --> 01:30:00,672
<i>Só 30% de energia restantes.</i>

1403
01:31:02,297 --> 01:31:03,672
Vocês estão bem?

1404
01:31:03,922 --> 01:31:04,838
Band-aid.

1405
01:31:05,088 --> 01:31:06,672
Duoduo, consegue se mexer?

1406
01:31:07,755 --> 01:31:10,463
Um, dois, três, segure-se.

1407
01:31:12,963 --> 01:31:14,172
Liu Qi!

1408
01:31:15,338 --> 01:31:17,297
Encontrou o problema?

1409
01:31:18,088 --> 01:31:19,547
